{
  "stem": "18581.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 276.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All the Jewish organizations, except the Communist Party-- the small, minute Communist Party of Lithuania, which had 900 members, and 2/3 of them Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All other organizations, like the labor Zionists, the [INAUDIBLE] Zionists, the-- the religious Zionists, the religious [INAUDIBLE] that was not Zionist, the Betar, revisionists-- all of them were declared illegal.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And their leadership was hunted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All the businesses were nationalized-- the bigger ones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The-- the fabrics, the factories, all industrial enterprises, 80% owned by Jews, were nationalized.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the bank accounts and the bank safes were nationalized-- again, 80%.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the banks themselves were all-- 80% of it was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what I would say is that the Soviets managed to break the economic back of the Jewish community, render them penniless, so it was easier for Hitler and-- to do what he did, with the help of local Lithuanians, collaborators.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they were, in many ways, robbed of their funds to resist, or to-- to bribe, or to, whatever, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- they started to-- changing courses, especially in economics.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They added courses of Marxism and Leninism.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it took them a long time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because Lithuanians are very-- even the-- the so-called Communists were, in fact, Lithuanian nationalists at heart.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everything went much slower than expected.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or not to the same extent as in Latvia and Estonia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think I [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think by the time we had to take the courses, the war broke out or something, or I went to hospital.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there were some courses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know, especially-- I think there was, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think I did take a-- a short course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which, of course, we all made fun of.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody took it seriously.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
